# Node image build context. The node Dockerfile builds only the C++ binary from
# src/ + CMakeLists.txt (BUILD_TESTING=OFF), so keep everything else out of the
# context — it keeps `docker build`/`docker compose build` fast and avoids
# shipping the gateway's stale target/ or the .git history into the image.
.git
gateway
deploy
docs
build
CMakeFiles
CMakeCache.txt
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
tests
*.o
*.out
kvstore
